{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO59048B1906P2D1N002387", "chronotag": "1762963931575", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "II-CF2387", "numeroOrdreDepot": "2387", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION_FIN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO59048B1906P2D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B1906", "triAmendement": "eaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaavhzwzzv", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA795998", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845514", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": ["PA842299", "PA605745", "PA842271"]}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "Mme&#160;K/Bidi,  M.&#160;Tjibaou, M.&#160;Sansu et M.&#160;Maurel"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "ETAT B", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 49", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 49", "type": "ANNEXE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": "ARTICLE 49", "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/1906C.asp#D_Etat_B"}, "missionVisee": {"codeEtat": "B", "codeMissionMinefi": "OA", "libelleMission": "Outre-mer", "missionRef": "3351"}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositifAmdtCreditPLF": {"listeProgrammes": {"programme": [{"libelle": "Emploi outre-mer", "programmeRef": "650375", "autorisationEngagement": "-4500000", "creditPaiement": "-4500000", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "Conditions de vie outre-mer", "programmeRef": "650377", "autorisationEngagement": "0", "creditPaiement": "0", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "Handicap et scolarit\u00e9 \u00e0 la R\u00e9union", "programmeRef": "650379", "autorisationEngagement": "4500000", "creditPaiement": "4500000", "action": "cr\u00e9ation", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}]}, "soldeAE": "0", "soldeCP": "0", "cpEgalAe": "true"}, "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Cet amendement cr&#x00E9;e le programme &#x00AB;&nbsp;Handicap et scolarit&#x00E9; &#x00E0; la R&#x00E9;union&nbsp;&#x00BB; et l&#x2019;abonde de 4&nbsp;500&nbsp;000&nbsp;&#x20AC; en AE et en CP provenant de l&#x2019;action 02 &#x00AB; Aide a&#x0300; l'insertion et a&#x0300; la qualification professionnelle &#x00BB; hors titre II du programme 138 &#x00AB; Soutien aux entreprises &#x00BB;.&nbsp;</p><p><br>Ce nouveau programme est destin&#x00E9; &#x00E0; la cr&#x00E9;ation de poste d&#x2019;accompagnants des &#x00E9;l&#x00E8;ves en situation de handicap (AESH) &#x00E0; l&#x2019;&#x00EE;le de la R&#x00E9;union.&nbsp;</p><p><br>Le 18&nbsp;octobre&nbsp;2025, le rectorat de la R&#x00E9;union a &#x00E9;t&#x00E9; condamn&#x00E9; par le tribunal administratif en raison du manque d&#x2019;AESH dans les &#x00E9;coles r&#x00E9;unionnaises.&nbsp;</p><p><br>Lors d&#x2019;une r&#x00E9;cente r&#x00E9;union avec les acteurs publics, le rectorat de la R&#x00E9;union admettait un manque de 212 AESH au sein de son acad&#x00E9;mie, privant ainsi de nombreux enfants handicap&#x00E9;s d&#x2019;un suivi n&#x00E9;cessaire &#x00E0; leur scolarit&#x00E9;.&nbsp;</p><p><br>Face &#x00E0; cette situation exceptionnelle pour un d&#x00E9;partement fran&#x00E7;ais, le pr&#x00E9;sent amendement vise &#x00E0; financer &#x00E0; hauteur du manque constat&#x00E9; le nombre de postes d&#x2019;AESH &#x00E0; la R&#x00E9;union.&nbsp;<br><br></p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-11-06", "datePublication": "2025-11-12", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Adopt\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2025-11-12T17:11:46+01:00", "sort": "Adopt\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO59048B1906P2D1N002387?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "3", "divisionCodeLoi": "R\u00e9union"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}